description:
Jared is back!... This 20 year old fraternity stud was excited to work with us again and we were excited to have him. This second time around, he told us that he wanted to put on a really good show for us, so he held off from hooking up with one of his girlfriends for a few days. We could tell, because he was hot and heavy for the entire shoot... you'll see what we mean.

We're glad to have Jared back. Watch him in three scenes- in the living room, then in the bathroom and shower, and finally in the bedroom.
title: Jared
